      <p>Stevie Hairspray-HamburgerHelper Nicks. Wow. She could be hiding one of your blackberry-oat scones in her hair. Speaking of scones, those look heavenly. I think scones have different purposes, there is the breakfast scone, flakey and crumbling and comforting and then there is the tea-time scone, tougher, dryer, and sturdier for those chilly winter afternoons. I myself am a fan of the biscuit style scones so you can be sure I&#39;ll be trying this recipe soon. Thank you!</p>
