    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Oatmeal-raspberry scones: the best. But for those foggy fall mornings I like the coffee/hazelnut scone we used to bake at the Uptown Espresso in Queen Anne. Roasted hazelnuts/buttermilk and espresso made the most amazing scones.  There is such easy potential in scones, one cannot resist playing around with whatever you have on hand.</p>
