  <li id="comment-29336" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Anonymous</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2011/08/it-still-surprises-me/#comment-29336"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2011-08-19T17:03:13-04:00">Friday, August 19, 2011 at 5:03 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
